00E9C0  2               ; perform SPRITESET sprite, field, value — set sprite register with vblank sync
00E9C0  2               ; Fields 0 (X) and 2 (Y) accept a signed word and write both lo/hi bytes.
00E9C0  2               ; All other fields accept a byte value.
00E9C0  2               ; Waits for vblank before writing to avoid visual glitching.
